# Common Rules

## Response Format

```json
{
  "data": {},
  "error": null
}
```

---

## Error Format

```json
{
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "message"
  }
}
```

---

## Status Code Policy

| Status | Meaning |
|---|---|
| 200 | Success |
| 400 | Validation Error |
| 401 | Unauthorized |
| 403 | Forbidden |
| 404 | Not Found |
| 500 | Internal Server Error |

